   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>To the salesman it means payment (...), to the rich man expenses. If the right cheek twitches, it means an unexpected offence. Make a propitiating sacrifice to Helios. If the left cheek twitches, it means something good. If the right jaw twitches, it means joy and something good.</ab>
